; Regression test for issue #698: When format_t outputs a balance, it should
; know the next line width.
;
; When a format string uses justify() on a multi-commodity balance, the
; continuation lines for additional commodities should be padded to the same
; width as the first commodity line.

2024/01/01 Test multi-commodity
    Assets:Stocks   10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Bonds    5 BOND @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash     -$2000.00

test bal --no-total --format '%(justify(scrub(display_total), 20, -1, true)) %(account)\n'
           $-2000.00
             10 AAPL
              5 BOND Assets
              5 BOND Assets:Bonds
           $-2000.00 Assets:Cash
             10 AAPL Assets:Stocks
end test
